config.paragraph: Into the summer breeze with all new designer dresses
Tasteful accessories walking a fine line between vintage and modern
Explore our new season with soft fabrics as if it's embracing a subtle forest breeze.

From classic leather jackets to high polish dress shoes, Fabrikam leather products only use the finest calf leather from Bivigliano, Italy. To ensure quality, we import directly from the farms and inspect every shipment by hand.
